{"tid":1930083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲士兵疑「行刑式」槍殺平民影片曝光　","createTime":"2020-03-17T10:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T10:33:34.000Z","uid":10540,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"be0382ca531f1fd1252cd917ce3d4340361c2ce3","tid":1930083,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:22:03.000Z","msg":"一名澳洲特種部隊士兵涉嫌在戰地、近距離槍殺一名手無寸鐵的阿富汗男子，國防部長對該段影片表示「深感不安」。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲廣播公司（ABC）在時事節目《四角》（Four Corners）上，播放一段2012年5月拍攝的影片。這段影片是由另一名特種部隊士兵的頭盔鏡頭攝製，顯示一名澳洲士兵在麥田中，槍殺一名阿富汗男子的情況。<br />\n<br />\n退役特種部隊士兵Braden Chapman在節目上表示，他被調派阿富汗期間，曾目擊三次類似事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在影片中，一位澳洲士兵用槍指向一名躺在地上的阿富汗男子。據畫面顯示，該名男子看似手無寸鐵，只拿著一串疑似祈禱念珠的東西。<br />\n<br />\n該名士兵三度向他的指揮官高呼：「你是否想我幹掉這個XX嗎？」隨後便在距離不足兩米範圍下，向他開了三槍。<br />\n<br />\n國防部長雷諾茲在聲明中表示：「我對今晚（3月16日）《四角》時事節目播放的內容深感不安」。<br />\n<br />\n她指會堅定地支持澳洲國防軍就澳洲特種部隊、在2005至2016年間的阿富汗行動展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/defence-minister-disturbed-over-sas-video-shooting\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Flanguage%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Fdefence-minister-disturbed-over-sas-video-shooting&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=025f2b60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/language/cantonese/zh-hant/defence-minister-disturbed-over-sas-video-shooting</a>"},{"pid":"3d6e7564145283ba7638f853201ee0e50021899a","tid":1930083,"uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:29:22.000Z","msg":"同香港皇軍一齊落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"97dbab3d45de462eb99ab219a27271d548cd9acf","tid":1930083,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:30:29.000Z","msg":"read<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3b7d3da073afdea8feeeddf3a77003093117c6","tid":1930083,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:31:14.000Z","msg":"又係美國"},{"pid":"7c0163810ef966d4cfee16ddefe8dd9492444953","tid":1930083,"uid":271894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jw632FF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjw632FF.jpg&h=a833c6ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港都有啊"},{"pid":"6b709d5f6424dd1839023301575ddd6c24525b35","tid":1930083,"uid":215876,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d3b7d3da073afdea8feeeddf3a77003093117c6","tid":1930083,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:31:14.000Z","msg":"又係美國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T10:33:34.000Z","msg":"又係香港警犬"}]}